Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀態好像是穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  他們說佳織恢復意識的機率幾乎為零
