Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:33.03,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)\pos(603,302)}『通向過去的大門』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後  我們根本就沒心思再辦天象館咖啡廳了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果直到那年的文化節結束都無所事事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之後  凪沙學姐又告訴我古川結轉學的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  偶爾也來一下學會露個臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.63,0:01:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學年主任很擔心你  老是問我「那傢伙將來的目標要怎麼辦」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  我也明白你的心情  但再不調整的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來會長決定好要做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決定要進內濱大學的理科學部了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我建議的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.77,0:01:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也打算做一些自己能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你的打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了尋找治好佳織的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定去讀醫學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考上醫大的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時離開了有著和佳織一起的回憶的家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大學裡我很快就碰壁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想讓佳織甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必須對大腦進行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對於採用對症療法的現代醫學來說是難以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腦是未知的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他部位有了損傷的話  可以移植
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理論上也是可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有腦是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  現在正在研究量子圖靈機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量子圖靈機？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高中的時候有個老師上課時經常扯到那個  不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那時候只覺得老師不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,概括地說就是把那個從理論轉化為實踐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡而言之  腦可能就是一台量子圖靈機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像是抓住了救命稻草一樣  研究量子論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至開始去研究量子控制論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我才知道這和詩織阿姨的研究有很大的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只聽說自從佳織出事後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨好像在熱衷於某項特別的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過了好幾年  佳織仍舊沉睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  在的話我就進來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好陰沉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借你的廚房用用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KENNY好像又寄來新的報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是關於宇宙弦向額外維空間延伸的時間逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像說夢話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟簡單說來就是回到過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真能做到  那個叫什麼時間悖論的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會引發什麼誰也不清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是凪沙學姐打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  令人懷念的我的母校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼要在這裡申請建新的研究所？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的地方也沒什麼不方便的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我常常帶到活動室來的黑色的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  記得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從當時開始大家就一直在研究那個盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是隨著調查的深入發現它在特定的地方才會有很強的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個地方就是這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且不惜廢棄學校也要繼續研究  太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個能再陪陪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡…是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華宮綜合研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡對那個黑盒子進行著研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外  在很多其他領域的研究上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也是世界上最尖端的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理  也歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨  那個東西馬上就能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是研究所裡進行著最高機密研究的部門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說  詩織阿姨她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我是研究團隊的成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是在研究什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想還是親眼看一看比較快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好厲害  簡直就像是SF一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個中間的地方就是最高機密？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是  古川嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是曾經叫做結的東西  這麼說比較妥當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結怎麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天  佳織遇到事故的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回到家後  發現結睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是機能停止運轉了  這樣說更加準確吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結  你已經回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要太擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作之進  作之進  拜託  快來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織跟我說她弄丟了  為什麼會在結這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結可能跟那場事故有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這為什麼成了最高機密？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說她不是人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單來說  她是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以現在的技術  她是不可能被造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她到底是誰製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然出現在內濱學園裡  又為什麼突然停止運轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡是些未知的迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  為什麼一直都瞞著我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時因為佳織的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有說出來的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,323)\fs18}AI Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們研究團隊發現那個叫做AI智能體的黑盒子對結有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結跟那個盒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在研究她的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了拯救佳織的一個可能的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了拯救佳織的可能的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結的人造生物器官非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內臟  血管  從神經系統到大腦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她的腦跟人類的腦有差不多的機能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼詩織阿姨找到的能救佳織的方法就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過研究她的身體  造一個新的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後把佳織移到那個身體裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把佳織移過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把大腦裡的信息  包括意識全部移植過去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量子圖靈機  但是那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情理論上可行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你們能參與這個研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和愛理從大學退了學  加入了詩織阿姨的團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了製造新的素體的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,323)\fs18}Yui's Unforced Intelligence system
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是結的主動智能系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名為YUIs工程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理主攻AI智能體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來研究結的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造結所用的技術是讓人震撼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究飛快地進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又過了幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於  新的人造素體誕生了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了這個時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始進行佐佐木佳織的意識轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始連接接口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認量子新腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始量子糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦波正常  心跳數正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素體的機能也開始運轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  信息轉移不進素體的人造大腦裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣  不應該會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下機器  終止移植
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除量子糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織的意識明明沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素體卻有了意識活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一素體已經無法用來移植了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨要去國外是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在北歐有個研究人造大腦的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詩織阿姨還沒放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那種方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人會怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山他也差不多該下結論了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然支倉小姐就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山他到現在為止一直都一心想著佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像完全沒注意到支倉小姐的感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為會因實驗失敗而告一段落呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女之間的關係就是這麼複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我就說三次元好煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  廣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙弦向額外維空間延伸的時間逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟簡單說來就是回到過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以現在的技術  她是不可能被造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  現在正在研究量子圖靈機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我常常帶到活動室來的黑色的盒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著調查的深入發現它在特定的地方才會有很強的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太愚蠢了  明明如此愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼每一個細節都嚴絲合縫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支倉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋山他還悶在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來啦  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是愛理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是睡在這種地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心身體吃不消哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有樣東西想給愛理看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織的素體被…  被整形成結的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變過去  從而拯救佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼改變過去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把結送到佳織出事之前那段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她阻止事故的發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會是在說時間移動這種虛構的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前KENNY送來的他那邊的研究人員的論文？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只不過是沒有任何依據的理論而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的相信有時間逆行這一回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結改變了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但世界也不過是產生了分歧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的佳織並不會被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界在分歧之後還是有會合的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會合？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因果的鎖鏈會修正這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而總有一天悖論也會就此消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因果的鎖鏈  這也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理你真的會相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理學家在世界的一隅每做一次貓的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙中的物理總量就會翻倍這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是多重世界詮釋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從宇宙總體那壓倒性的物質量來看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只要花數十年就可以恢復的誤差而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要資料遺失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並從研究人員的記憶中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界便將再次會合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了資源的有效利用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有力量使產生分歧的世界再度會合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是自然的規律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說這就是因果的鎖鏈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  但是想要用這個方法回到過去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接收的地方也必須要有個量子傳送裝置才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AI智能體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個盒子會在特定的地點發出細微的量子震動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而反應最強烈的地方就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舊校舍的五樓原本是電梯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是結出現的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底結到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由不可能實現的技術創造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會對被稱為AI智能體的黑盒子產生反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她究竟是為了什麼而出現的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的呢  動機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候真的喪失記憶了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那奇怪的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我的假說中的推論全部相吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你沒瘋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了  結
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球儀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes  地球儀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險  真的好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的空氣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在地面上看見的星辰的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前發出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說你看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙女座銀河距離地球是239萬光年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在所見到的是239萬年前的光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和239萬年相比  14年只不過是眨眼一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間拖得越長  和過去的距離就會變得越遠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所需的能量也會變得更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的模擬演示相比
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的進程比想像的慢了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒精神了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼成功不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說最初的結是誰做出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AI智能體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始果然還是分析了那個盒子之後的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  應該是詩織阿姨做出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那AI智能體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個量子圖靈機也許就是記錄多重世界的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和阿克夏記錄差不多的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會對身為分歧點的結產生反應
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了結以外的人則不被允許做時間逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為記錄點…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是記錄點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:20:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在要把你送回到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任務是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從10月14日發生的事故中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出佐佐木佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就留在這裡看門了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就分頭調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織…
